                     <interp inst="t17820515-19-defend187" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17820515-19-off83" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820515-19-off83" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820515-19-off83" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing 49 yards of worsted binding lace, 71 yards of seaming worsted lace, 36 yards of seaming one edge lace, 24 worsted roses, 6 pair of worsted glass-strings and holders, 4 pair of worsted strings, 12 yards of broad plain white worsted lace, 24 yards of binding white worsted lace, 12 yards of broad plain drab worsted lace, 24 yards of binding drab worsted lace, 4 yards of broad drab worsted lace, 2 pair of glass-string trimmings, 2 sets of worsted footmen's holders, 2 pieces of green spring curtain lines, and a set of orange worsted footmen's holders, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820515-19-victim189" type="victimName">
                           David 
                           Lyall
